[
  {
    "text": "A really common question we're getting in",
    "start": 1642.48,
    "end": 1645.12,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "the chat is about the decision in Canada",
    "start": 1645.44,
    "end": 1648.24,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "to delay the second",
    "start": 1648.24,
    "end": 1649.48,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "dose up to four months.",
    "start": 1649.52,
    "end": 1651.44,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "This was based off a recommendation from",
    "start": 1652.04,
    "end": 1654.32,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "the from NACI, the",
    "start": 1654.32,
    "end": 1655.68,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "National Advisory Committee",
    "start": 1655.72,
    "end": 1656.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "for Immunizations.",
    "start": 1656.92,
    "end": 1657.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "I think that's the full acronym.",
    "start": 1657.88,
    "end": 1660.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "Doctor Sharma can I get your insights on this one?",
    "start": 1662.16,
    "end": 1665.72,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "Sure, so",
    "start": 1667.28,
    "end": 1668,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean the first part of it is that",
    "start": 1668,
    "end": 1669.36,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "that NACI is, as I said",
    "start": 1669.36,
    "end": 1671.08,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "in my presentation, independent and",
    "start": 1671.08,
    "end": 1673.8,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "it's not part of Health Canada.",
    "start": 1673.84,
    "end": 1675.2,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm getting a lot of emails telling me",
    "start": 1675.2,
    "end": 1677.2,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "that I shouldn't have made that decision.",
    "start": 1677.2,
    "end": 1678.48,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "I didn't, just to be clear.",
    "start": 1678.48,
    "end": 1680.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "The Health Canada position",
    "start": 1680.8,
    "end": 1681.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "is what's in the product monograph, so",
    "start": 1682,
    "end": 1683.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "we still from the Health Canada",
    "start": 1684,
    "end": 1685.48,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "perspective are saying a 21 day",
    "start": 1685.48,
    "end": 1687.52,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "interval for Pfizer, 28 day for",
    "start": 1687.52,
    "end": 1689.6,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "Moderna and then between four weeks",
    "start": 1689.64,
    "end": 1692.28,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "and 12 weeks for AstraZeneca.",
    "start": 1692.28,
    "end": 1694.32,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "And what NACI does, though is give those",
    "start": 1694.64,
    "end": 1697.12,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "recommendations on how best to use",
    "start": 1697.12,
    "end": 1699.32,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "the vaccines and when they look at",
    "start": 1699.36,
    "end": 1701.4,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "them, they looked",
    "start": 1701.44,
    "end": 1702,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "at obviously the clinical trial data.",
    "start": 1702.04,
    "end": 1703.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "They looked at real-world data.",
    "start": 1704.36,
    "end": 1706.4,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "We have data from",
    "start": 1706.44,
    "end": 1708.56,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "other countries that have actually used a",
    "start": 1708.6,
    "end": 1710.6,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "longer dosing interval. At the time",
    "start": 1710.6,
    "end": 1712.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "that they looked at it,",
    "start": 1712.76,
    "end": 1713.44,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "there was a lot of data around an 8 week",
    "start": 1713.44,
    "end": 1715.64,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "interval between the 1st and",
    "start": 1715.64,
    "end": 1716.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "2nd doses of the mRNA vaccines, and of course for",
    "start": 1716.88,
    "end": 1720.72,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "AstraZeneca we already",
    "start": 1720.84,
    "end": 1721.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "have that kind of longer",
    "start": 1721.88,
    "end": 1723.12,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "interval in the clinical trials.",
    "start": 1723.12,
    "end": 1724.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "They were also looking at",
    "start": 1725.16,
    "end": 1726.2,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "what they knew about vaccines in general.",
    "start": 1726.2,
    "end": 1729.36,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "And we know that when you have",
    "start": 1729.4,
    "end": 1730.84,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "immunity, especially at",
    "start": 1730.88,
    "end": 1731.92,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "these high levels,",
    "start": 1731.92,
    "end": 1733.16,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "that Dr. Gommerman talked about,",
    "start": 1733.16,
    "end": 1735.36,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "they don't just immediately sort of",
    "start": 1735.36,
    "end": 1736.56,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "fall off a cliff all of a sudden.",
    "start": 1736.56,
    "end": 1738.16,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "So we don't know how long they last.",
    "start": 1738.16,
    "end": 1742.2,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "We are getting more information on",
    "start": 1742.2,
    "end": 1743.6,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "how sustained that immune response is,",
    "start": 1743.6,
    "end": 1745.64,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "but we do know that you've",
    "start": 1745.72,
    "end": 1746.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "already got a high level.",
    "start": 1746.96,
    "end": 1748.24,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not going to",
    "start": 1748.24,
    "end": 1748.8,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "drop off very quickly, so they",
    "start": 1748.8,
    "end": 1750.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "use that along with some modeling,",
    "start": 1750.8,
    "end": 1752.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "and then this is the important part,",
    "start": 1752.96,
    "end": 1754.6,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "amd looked at what the supply",
    "start": 1754.64,
    "end": 1756,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "situation would be in Canada.",
    "start": 1756.04,
    "end": 1757.56,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "So this is the part that's a bit,",
    "start": 1757.88,
    "end": 1759.68,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "I think, challenging for",
    "start": 1759.72,
    "end": 1760.92,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "people. So they took a look at",
    "start": 1760.92,
    "end": 1763.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "what the benefits were",
    "start": 1763.8,
    "end": 1765.2,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "of getting first doses",
    "start": 1765.32,
    "end": 1766.6,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "into as many people as possible",
    "start": 1766.6,
    "end": 1768.36,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "versus sticking to a shorter",
    "start": 1768.44,
    "end": 1770.56,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "interval and potentially then",
    "start": 1770.76,
    "end": 1773.68,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "having more people",
    "start": 1773.88,
    "end": 1774.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "having completed vaccination",
    "start": 1774.96,
    "end": 1777.08,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "schedules and",
    "start": 1777.08,
    "end": 1778.8,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "having some people that don't.",
    "start": 1778.8,
    "end": 1780.64,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "And so their recommendation was",
    "start": 1780.68,
    "end": 1782.56,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "that you could go up to and",
    "start": 1782.84,
    "end": 1785.4,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll just say that",
    "start": 1785.4,
    "end": 1785.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "again, up to four months",
    "start": 1785.88,
    "end": 1787.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "in their opinion,",
    "start": 1787.88,
    "end": 1788.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "without compromising the immune response.",
    "start": 1788.96,
    "end": 1791.4,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "They didn't say that you have to, so",
    "start": 1791.48,
    "end": 1793.72,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "I know a lot of places are",
    "start": 1793.72,
    "end": 1794.68,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "automatically giving that second vaccination dose",
    "start": 1794.72,
    "end": 1800.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "exactly four months later.",
    "start": 1800.96,
    "end": 1802.24,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "That's not what they said. They were saying, you could,",
    "start": 1802.28,
    "end": 1804.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "if it's for, you know,",
    "start": 1804.76,
    "end": 1805.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "in your best interest to get more",
    "start": 1805.92,
    "end": 1807.12,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "people vaccinated, you could go",
    "start": 1807.12,
    "end": 1809.08,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "up to four months. Now what they're doing",
    "start": 1809.12,
    "end": 1811.56,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "is that they're also looking at",
    "start": 1811.6,
    "end": 1813.32,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "new data that's come out that's showing",
    "start": 1813.36,
    "end": 1815.84,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "that potentially there might",
    "start": 1815.84,
    "end": 1816.84,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "be some differences",
    "start": 1816.84,
    "end": 1818.04,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "in some of the subgroups, so",
    "start": 1818.08,
    "end": 1820.24,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "people that might have a bit of",
    "start": 1820.28,
    "end": 1821.64,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "a compromised immune",
    "start": 1821.68,
    "end": 1822.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "system, such as people that had cancer",
    "start": 1822.76,
    "end": 1824.48,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "and received treatment,",
    "start": 1824.48,
    "end": 1825.64,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "whether or not in the",
    "start": 1825.72,
    "end": 1826.84,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "elderly population so 70 and older,",
    "start": 1826.84,
    "end": 1829.52,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "80 and older.",
    "start": 1829.56,
    "end": 1831.44,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe their immunity",
    "start": 1831.48,
    "end": 1832.48,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "drops off a bit quicker than",
    "start": 1832.48,
    "end": 1833.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "other groups, so they're actually",
    "start": 1833.96,
    "end": 1835.44,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "in the process of looking at",
    "start": 1835.44,
    "end": 1836.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "that as well now",
    "start": 1836.76,
    "end": 1838.4,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "and to see if they need to",
    "start": 1838.44,
    "end": 1840.2,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "update that recommendation in any way.",
    "start": 1840.48,
    "end": 1842.6,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "So we've got the Health Canada",
    "start": 1842.64,
    "end": 1846.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "sort of strict interpretation of the data,",
    "start": 1846.88,
    "end": 1849.2,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "whether it's clinical trial,",
    "start": 1849.24,
    "end": 1850.44,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "real-world evidence, and then",
    "start": 1850.44,
    "end": 1851.48,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "we have this, like",
    "start": 1851.48,
    "end": 1852.56,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "how do we best use",
    "start": 1852.56,
    "end": 1855,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "these vaccines in Canada",
    "start": 1855,
    "end": 1856.96,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "to protect us all",
    "start": 1857.12,
    "end": 1858.64,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "in the best ways we can get",
    "start": 1858.72,
    "end": 1860.72,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, back to some state",
    "start": 1860.92,
    "end": 1862.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "of normality as quickly",
    "start": 1862.76,
    "end": 1864.32,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "as possible, so that's",
    "start": 1864.32,
    "end": 1865.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "where that came from.",
    "start": 1865.76,
    "end": 1866.44,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "But again, I just want to underscore that",
    "start": 1866.44,
    "end": 1868.04,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "it's up to four months and",
    "start": 1868.08,
    "end": 1869.76,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "it's really dependent on availability",
    "start": 1869.76,
    "end": 1871.44,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "of vaccines, and it might change based",
    "start": 1871.44,
    "end": 1873.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "on evidence, which you know",
    "start": 1873.88,
    "end": 1875.08,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "is challenging in and of itself,",
    "start": 1875.08,
    "end": 1876.56,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "when we change recommendations.",
    "start": 1876.56,
    "end": 1877.88,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "But just to say that that's",
    "start": 1878,
    "end": 1879.16,
    "is_final": true,
    "speaker_id": 0
  },
  {
    "text": "what they're looking at",
    "start": 1879.16,
    "end": 1879.88,
